Swiss Stocks Snap Three-Day Decline; Credit Suisse, UBS Shares Lead Gains

-- B y   A n d r e w   R u m m e r
-- 
2011-07-13T07:27:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-13/swiss-stocks-snap-three-day-decline-credit-suisse-ubs-shares-lead-gains.html
Swiss stocks rose, halting a three-
day slide, as Credit Suisse Group AG and UBS AG advanced. The
benchmark Swiss Market Index gained 0.5 percent to 6,045.66 at
9:25 a.m. in Zurich, having earlier lost 0.3 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
